lid; background-color: #ccc;">times</a> about PSUS, but here I want to poin=
t out that there are two very ambitious elements to Ackman=E2=80=99s pitch,=
=C2=A0<em>size=C2=A0</em>and=C2=A0<em>price: </em>He wants to raise $25 bil=
lion, and he wants the fund to trade at a premium to its net asset value.=
=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Trading at a premium=C2=A0is ambitio=
