StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #00000=
0; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-botto=
m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">chea=
p but lucrative=C2=A0bet against credit</a> just before Covid-19 hit =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0and they are much of what you pay for if you hire him as your hedg=
e fund manager.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Ackman is good at =
social media and has a large retail following, and if there is one single m=
ost important lesson from the last few years in financial markets, it is th=
at stocks with large retail followings on social media can sustainably trad=
e at a large premium to their intrinsic value.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">That last point is the most obvious one. =E2=80=9CThere is a meme=
-stock element to all of this,=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/36079366.196399/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vc=
GluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDYtMDYvYmlsbC1hY2ttYW4td2FudHMtYS1sb3Qtb2YteW91=
ci1tb25leT9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNzE2MjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9=
zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDA3MTYmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1Zm=
Y/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC2476008c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"it=
emscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !=
important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-b=
ottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">I wrote last month</a>, and th=
e Financial Times says<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-1" styl=
