<span>[1]</span>
</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ackman referred to his so=
cial media following and heavy media coverage as =E2=80=9Cnotoriety=E2=80=
=9D in the presentation. =E2=80=9CI have built up a large base of instituti=
onal and retail followers that follow our every move=E2=80=89.=E2=80=89.=E2=
=80=89.=E2=80=89Media interest is valuable in attracting investor interest =
and also in creating liquidity for our shareholders,=E2=80=9D he said.</p><=
p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Pershing Square USA is registered as a so-calle=
d 40 Act fund, which carries fewer regulatory restrictions on communication=
s than Pershing Square Holdings.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CT=
he fund is just geared to retail,=E2=80=9D said one investment manager who =
has spoken with Ackman. =E2=80=9CHe can have direct engagement in the US, t=
hat=E2=80=99s why he thinks it will trade up. He wasn=E2=80=99t allowed to =
tweet about his London-listed fund,=E2=80=9D added the investor.</p></block=
quote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But Ackman=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<em>size=C2=A0=
