=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The=C2=A0company pays you back $665 pe=
r month for the next 30 years.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I mean=
,=C2=A0<em>probably=C2=A0</em>the annuity is more like =E2=80=9Cthe company=
