=C2=A0you could just give me your $100,000, and I could pay you back over 3=
0 years =E2=80=94=C2=A0but that would require a lot of work.</p><p style=3D=
"margin: 16px 0;">Here is what a bank account is:</p><ol style=3D"list-styl=
