 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">I love them all</a>:<=
/p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Deutsche Bank AG is encouraging=
 its investment bankers to be more selective in pitching for mergers and ac=
quisitions mandates and focus on more profitable deals, people with knowled=
ge of the matter said, following a recent hiring spree at the firm.</p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">While the German lender plans to continue to work =
with both large and small- to medium-sized firms, its investment bankers ha=
ve been urged to prioritize winning mandates for bigger M&amp;A deals, the =
people said. The move highlights the bank=E2=80=99s efforts to improve effi=
